DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260711
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260712
SUMMARY:🌲 J04 - Mariposa Grove (séquoias) → Sweetwater
DESCRIPTION:08h00 Départ High Sierra RV (check-out avant 11h)\nRoute vers Mariposa Grove (entrée sud Yosemite\, CA-41)\n10h00 Parking Welcome Plaza (limite 25 ft pour RV)\n10h00-11h10 Mariposa Grove - boucle courte (~1h10) : Grizzly Giant\, California Tunnel Tree\nOU 09h30-12h45 Mariposa Grove - boucle longue (~3h15)\n12h00 Pique-nique (parking Wawona)\n12h00 Route → Sweetwater Campground (Stanislaus NF\, ~1-2h)\n14h00 Check-in Sweetwater Campground\nTunnel View + Mist Trail + El Capitan prévus au Jour 5\n🏕️ Sweetwater Campground - conf. reservation-camping-11-07.pdf
CATEGORIES:Programme
