DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260715
SUMMARY:🌋 J07 - Death Valley (Badwater\, Artist Drive\, Zabriskie) → Valley of Fire
DESCRIPTION:05h30 Réveil + départ Furnace Creek (lever soleil 06h34)\n06h00-07h00 ⭐⭐⭐ Badwater Basin (-86m\, croûte de sel)\n07h00-08h00 ⭐⭐⭐ Artist Drive (route panoramique 14km\, sens unique\, RV ≤25ft OK)\n08h00-10h00 ⭐⭐⭐ Golden Canyon (rando ~3km\, 1h30-2h\, Red Cathedral)\n10h00-11h00 Déjeuner Furnace Creek Visitor Center\n11h00-11h30 ⭐⭐⭐ Zabriskie Point (badlands multicolores)\n11h30-12h00 Dante's View (option\, 1669m\, vérifier limite RV)\n14h00-17h00 Route → Valley of Fire (CA-160/I-15/NV-169\, ~280 km)\n17h00-19h00 ⭐⭐ Rando autour Atlatl Rock Campground (roches rouges)\n🏕️ Atlatl Rock Campground - Valley of Fire State Park - conf. reservation-camping-14-07.pdf
